text: Jamal Ben Saddik ( born October 3, 1990) is a Belgian- Moroccanhttps://www.brusselstimes.com/344050/antwerp-bans-opening-of-gym- owned-by-famous-kickboxerhttps://nltimes.nl/2024/03/10/rico-verhoeven-wins- kickboxing-tournament professional kickboxer.
